     <!-- Display the Title as a link to the Post's permalink. -->
 	<h1 class="post-title"><a href="http://www.southernmissradio.com/about-wusm" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to About WUSM">About WUSM</a></h1>
    
 
    <span class="border"></span>
    
 	<div class="entry">
   		<p>WUSM-FM (88.5 fm) broadcasts from the Hattiesburg campus of the University of Southern Mississippi. WUSM celebrates American roots music with a strong Mississippi influence from a 60,000 plus music library. WUSM&#8217;s programming can be found streaming on the Internet at  www.SouthernMissRadio.com.</p>
<p>WUSM can be reached by phone at (601) 266-4287, and by e-mail at <a id="Email link to WUSM" title="Email WUSM" href="mailto:wusm@usm.edu">wusm@usm.edu</a>. Our address is 118 College Drive Box #5121, Hattiesburg MS 39406. Our offices are located in College Hall, suites 106, 302, and 303.  For underwriting opportunities, you may call our main office at 601-266-4287 or email us at <a href="mailto:wusm.usm.edu">wusm.usm.edu</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>General Manager, Justin Martin, (601) 266-5696.  <a href="mailto:wusm@usm.edu">wusm@usm.edu</a></p>
<p>Lesley Sanders-Wood, Sales Manager   <a href="mailto:Lesley.Sanders@usm.edu">Lesley.Sanders@usm.edu</a>   601-266-5188</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Information for FCC licensing data on WUSM may be obtained by clicking the FCC logo.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.fcc.gov"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-94" title="FCC Logo" alt="FCC Logo" src="/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/fcclogowords1.jpg" width="165" height="56" /></a></p>
        
         	</div>
    
